{"type":"question","id":29544,"title":"天朝的最后一期新闻联播会是什么样子？","uid":54381,"topics":[2423,163],"contents":"新闻联播大结局是什么样<br>\nsqchen2015-09-23 01:20:12<br>\n1990年12月14日晚7：30，德国统一两个月之后，在民主德国播出近40年之久的新闻联播类节目Aktuelle Kamera（时事聚焦）迎来了自己的最后一期。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9EaXNOT1dFLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/DisNOWE.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DisNOWE.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/DisNOWE.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n主持该节目二十余年的播音员Wolfgang Meyer面色凝重，语调阴沉地开始播音。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9SQWFyMlFjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RAar2Qc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RAar2Qc.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RAar2Qc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>女士们先生们晚上好（恩社会主义东德也使用资产阶级的称呼）</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n当日的新闻还是蛮丰富的，比如欧共体罗马峰会讨论东欧改革援助问题<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9yeG82UDJkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rxo6P2d.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rxo6P2d.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rxo6P2d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>hilfe=救命啊</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n昂纳克抗议关押被驳回<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS94dzM0Qmp4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xw34Bjx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xw34Bjx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xw34Bjx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>昂书记黑框眼镜同款价钱公道柏林莱比锡包邮</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n阿尔巴尼亚暴乱<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS96NU9FZ0lKLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/z5OEgIJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/z5OEgIJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/z5OEgIJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>阿尔巴尼亚不属于包邮地区</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n最后一条新闻是戈尔巴乔夫会见韩国总统卢泰愚<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9qRjBJUGxuLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jF0IPln.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jF0IPln.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jF0IPln.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n播完之后，主持人宣布最后一期新闻联播全部结束<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9mcUx0RnFqLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fqLtFqj.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fqLtFqj.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fqLtFqj.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>新闻联播，永别了</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n之后一段短片回顾了新闻联播以及德意志民主共和国的历史。此处用了一段相当怪异的背景音乐，间杂夸张的笑声，似乎是在说：你国四十年的XX主义历史就是个笑话<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS96SFRpSDV4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zHTiH5x.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zHTiH5x.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zHTiH5x.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tSkFHMGxZLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mJAG0lY.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mJAG0lY.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mJAG0lY.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS80YXJFN3dMLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/4arE7wL.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4arE7wL.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/4arE7wL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8yQ2ttb1UzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2CkmoU3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2CkmoU3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2CkmoU3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9iWjBJcTJELmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bZ0Iq2D.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bZ0Iq2D.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bZ0Iq2D.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n下面嘛，就是天气预报呗<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.mohu.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9DTWF2R1NKLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CMavGSJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CMavGSJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/CMavGSJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n女背景声在介绍新的新闻节目的播出时间，但是屏幕上的字表示东德的编导们很不爽<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<center>失望！愤怒！恐惧！不过都是自找的。</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n再下面呢？再下面真的没了。南柯一梦，大戏收场，曲终人散。<br>\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lVNu5lAzeZc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">东德版最后一期新闻联播全集</a>","date":"2020-08-08","agreeCount":40,"discussionCount":3}